I11(f) T4Audits of Credit Facilities of the Federal Reserve System._

I12(1) T4DefinitionsK._In this subsection, the following definitions shall apply:

I13(A) T4Credit facilityK._The term ``credit facility'' means a program or facility, including any special purpose vehicle or other entity established by or on behalf of the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System or a Federal reserve bank, authorized by the Board of Governors under section 13(3) of the Federal Reserve Act (12 U.S.C. 343), that is not subject to audit under subsection (e).

I13(B) T4Covered transactionK._The term ``covered transaction'' means any open market transaction or discount window advance that meets the definition of ``covered transaction'' in section 11(s) of the Federal Reserve Act.

