I89. Transparency of programs, priority goals, and results

I11(a) T4Transparency of Agency Programs._

I12(1) T4In generalK._Not later than October 1, 2012, the Office of Management and Budget shall_

I13(A) ensure the effective operation of a single website;

I13(B) at a minimum, update the website on a quarterly basis; and

I13(C) include on the website information about each program identified by the agencies.

