I22``(2) T4DatabasesK._At a minimum and before issuing any payment and award, each agency shall review as appropriate the following databases to verify eligibility of the payment and award:

I23``(A) The Death Master File of the Social Security Administration.

I23``(B) The General Services Administration's Excluded Parties List System.

