I23``(A) use of the databases described under subsection (a)(2); and

I23``(B) use of other databases designated by the Director of the Office of Management and Budget in consultation with agencies and in accordance with paragraph (2).

I22``(2) T4Other databasesK._In making designations of other databases under paragraph (1)(B), the Director of the Office of Management and Budget shall_

