I21Memorandum of President of the United States, June 29, 1995, 60 F.R. 35113, provided:

I21Memorandum for the Secretary of the Treasury

I21On January 31, 1995, I approved a program of assistance to Mexico, in the form of swap facilities and securities guarantees in an amount not to exceed $20 billion, using the Exchange Stabilization Fund (the ``ESF program'').

