I21I hereby delegate to you the reporting requirement contained in section 406 of Public Law 104ÿ096 [set out above]. You are authorized and requested to report this certification immediately to the Speaker of the House and appropriate congressional committees, as defined in section 407 of Public Law 104ÿ096 [set out above].

