I12(7) the retirement and disability files of the United States Coast Guard, the Tennessee Valley Authority, the Commissioned Corps of the Public Health Service, the Commissioned Corps of the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration, and the Foreign Service;

I12(8) the insurance claims files of the Federal Emergency Management Agency and the Department of Agriculture;

