I89. Investigations and reviews

I11(a) T4Investigations by Secretary._

I12(1) T4In generalK._The Secretary shall within a reasonable time limit_

I13(A) carry out an investigation and make a finding after receiving a complaint referred to in section 6716(b), a determination by a State or local administrative agency, or other information about a possible violation of this chapter;

