I11(c) Each audit conducted pursuant to subsection (a) shall be conducted by an independent auditor in accordance with generally accepted government auditing standards, except that, for the purposes of this chapter, performance audits shall not be required except as authorized by the Director.

I11(d) Each single audit conducted pursuant to subsection (a) for any fiscal year shall_

