I89. Taxpayer identifying number

I11(a) In this section_

I12(1) ``included Federal loan program'' has the same meaning given that term in section 6103(T3lK)(3)(C) of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 (26 U.S.C. 6103(T3lK)(3)(C)).

